{"tid":383551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[勵志]肥婆做運動三個月，激減50磅","createTime":"2017-09-01T14:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T15:05:38.000Z","uid":95418,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5afb6a44184cd31bdcb560120ba67d26632ad41f","tid":383551,"uid":95418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:42:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，次次一聽我個肥婆朋友講做運動就火都黎。佢係出面健身會每個月俾成千幾二千蚊個教練，正係佢教啲拉根同瑜珈動作。我本身操開跑步游水，所以我身為絲都幾明白減肥係一定要靠帶氧運動。次次我都叫佢唔好浪費咁多錢俾人，跟我去跑下步游下水。但佢對我嘅說話永遠唔會聽入耳。重要成日同我講佢瘦左，但我一啲都唔覺囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日我忍唔住佢講左我唔覺你瘦左，佢就對我發火。我講真話姐，佢就發曬火咁，到宜家佢重唔理我添。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉，同佢初中玩到而家，我真係好關心佢，唔想無左呢位朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n忽相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae8a07aa749236373863f04c7687affa46bb50b7","tid":383551,"uid":95418,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"肥婆成日話我食唔肥先咁瘦，<br />\n我係你地面乜都食，但係背後我戒曬口你又知唔知呀<br />\n你一個星期做一次運動，post曬上ig Snapchat話曬俾全世界人聽你減肥咁，但我一個星期做三日運動你又知唔知呀。<br />\n正係識走精面，零成效。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講個事實出黎你又嬲。<br />\n肥婆真係麻煩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4baab019f2e6b89d6d470a43ee5a856b3b6e57","tid":383551,"uid":70840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:02:25.000Z","msg":"銀包激減50磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b441950669eb5a189893c27614b936b9a625470a","tid":383551,"uid":33568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:03:08.000Z","msg":"真心？"},{"pid":"f7e71767841ed429a2c95180a44e385e8611e6c6","tid":383551,"uid":95418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T15:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心？</blockquote><br />\n真心post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}